dc_title_s: Railroad map of Wisconsin prepared for the railroad commissioner by Allan D. Conover C.E.

dc_description_s: Includes table of railroad lines with mileage in Wisconsin and total mileage Dec. 31, 1887.. 1 map: col.; 86 x 68 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
